headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific Expands Real-World Data Interoperability and Linkage Through Strategic Collaboration with Datavant
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., February 11, 2026--Thermo Fisher Scientific, the world leader in serving science, today announced a strategic data collaboration with Datavant, the data collaboration platform trusted for healthcare, to make it easier for pharmaceutical and biotech companies to connect real-world data with clinical research—helping them generate stronger evidence, faster.
